I really am.

27
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:16,140
Still take it. You never know.

28
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,570
Are you really leaving?

29
00:02:20,570 --> 00:02:22,560
Why don't you stay a bit longer?

30
