You should rest today.

32
00:02:27,170 --> 00:02:30,250
We can be together from now on.

33
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:35,280
Okay. You should rest at home, too.

34
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,670
Thank you.

35
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,090
See you tomorrow.

36
00:03:00,810 --> 00:03:02,520
Get home safely.

37
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,790
Call me when you arrive.

38
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,710
I can't.

39
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:36,730
I can't let you go.

40
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,730
Please stay with me.

41
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,360
What's wrong?

42
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:12,050
When did I fall asleep?

43
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:32,730
Baek Su Jeong.

44
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:34,820
Dad, you're up.

45
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:38,340
The thing is, I need to go back to work—

46
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:41,170
Were you with the director?

47
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:46,450
Are you back together?

48
00:05:47,570 --> 00:05:49,200
Yes.

49
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,980
Su Jeong, his family isn't a normal family.

50
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:54,060
According to the article, many eyes are on him.

51
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:55,840
A lot of people are talking.

52
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:59,790
You know I don't care about stuff like that.

53
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:05,390
I really like him a lot.

54
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:08,710
So, can't you just allow it?

55
00:06:14,090 --> 00:06:16,450
What do you mean allow?

56
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:21,840
I should trust your decision.

57
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,450
But, Su Jeong,

58
00:06:24,450 --> 00:06:26,840
tell me you're having a hard time.

59
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,700
Don't just hold it in.

60
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:30,750
I don't care about anything else.

61
00:06:31,590 --> 00:06:33,670
I just want you to be happy.

62
00:06:33,670 --> 00:06:35,560
That's enough.

63
00:06:37,340 --> 00:06:38,920
Okay.

64
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,500
Whatever. Go to work now.

65
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:42,800
Okay, I will.

66
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:45,350
But sleeping outside is...

67
00:06:47,050 --> 00:06:49,030
Just don't get caught.

68
00:06:49,030 --> 00:06:51,750
Okay, I'll never get caught.

69
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:55,970
Say you won't stay out all night!

70
