71
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,430
 Director Ban. 

72
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,530
Yes.

73
00:07:16,530 --> 00:07:20,300
 You're dismissed as of today. 

74
00:07:37,610 --> 00:07:40,640
I knew this would happen.

75
00:07:42,210 --> 00:07:47,440
Didn't you say there was nothing going on?

76
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,310
 Yes, Chairwoman. 

77
00:07:50,210 --> 00:07:52,190
 It seems clear... 

78
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:55,570
 there is nothing going on between them. 

79
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:59,780
I'm sorry for disappointing you.

80
